{"type":"tool_execution_end","toolCallId":"call_065d56e0501b455686687759","toolName":"mcp","result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C9\ncase_id: arb-ex11a-20260619213136\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:2:C9\nremaining_ms: 887847\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex11a-20260619213136\",\"member_id\":\"C9\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"evidence\":[{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-19T21:43:22Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_089fa1cded7e_submitted-evidence-06-defendant-089fa1cded7e\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-06-defendant-089fa1cded7e.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Provides a same-database contrast between a true Tehran FIR airspace closure (A0225/26, QAFLC, Airspace Restrictions, Tehran FIR closed to all flights except approved international civil arrivals/departures) and plaintiff's A1010/26 airport-operations NOTAM (QFALC).\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-19T21:44:40Z\",\"sha256\":\"089fa1cded7e8c89534b9ad19009ed8c1f08a2158a3529ce7af26b482cba7251\",\"size_bytes\":1234,\"source_description\":\"Notamify page for OIIX A0225/26, the January 2026 Tehran FIR closure matching the market packet's qualifying example, captured by web.open during defendant merits investigation.\",\"source_url\":\"https://notamify.com/notams/OIIX/823cf1a7-690b-446d-ad8f-90b9725d7408\",\"storage_name\":\"08/089fa1cded7e8c89534b9ad19009ed8c1f08a2158a3529ce7af26b482cba7251\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"defendant\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Notamify January 2026 Tehran FIR closure comparison\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-19T21:39:35Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_0beb299b6e6b_submitted-evidence-04-plaintiff-0beb299b6e6b\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-04-plaintiff-0beb299b6e6b.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Aviation-risk context showing western Tehran FIR remained closed in June 2026 after the broader Iran airspace crisis, supporting the significance of western OIIX restrictions.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-19T21:39:30Z\",\"sha256\":\"0beb299b6e6b0349185b5e71aca80cc33294fe94f39e17b97ed9c9bd9aba9b1d\",\"size_bytes\":1302,\"source_description\":\"SafeAirspace Iran page captured via web.open/find during plaintiff merits investigation.\",\"source_url\":\"https://safeairspace.net/iran/\",\"storage_name\":\"0b/0beb299b6e6b0349185b5e71aca80cc33294fe94f39e17b97ed9c9bd9aba9b1d\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"SafeAirspace Iran OIIX western FIR context\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-19T21:39:21Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_60a74d32aeaf_submitted-evidence-03-plaintiff-60a74d32aeaf\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-03-plaintiff-60a74d32aeaf.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Independent corroborating report that Iran's CAA issued a NOTAM closing all airports in western Tehran FIR except limited daylight operations and suspending prior permissions.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-19T21:39:20Z\",\"sha256\":\"60a74d32aeafd272e910e4ff7923c9a220ed86c135e18008615832b36772b3b6\",\"size_bytes\":1454,\"source_description\":\"Arab Times article captured via web.open during plaintiff merits investigation.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.arabtimesonline.com/news/iran-suspends-flight-permissions-restricts-western-airspace-access/\",\"storage_name\":\"60/60a74d32aeafd272e910e4ff7923c9a220ed86c135e18008615832b36772b3b6\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Arab Times May 23 2026 CAA NOTAM report\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-19T21:39:05Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_a701f560aa64_submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-a701f560aa64\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-a701f560aa64.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Corroborates that Iran's Civil Aviation Authority issued NOTAM OIIX A1010/26 closing western Tehran FIR airports from May 22 to May 25 and requiring fresh approvals.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-19T21:39:10Z\",\"sha256\":\"a701f560aa648b724e0f3c4e0435fc666cb1905bad5650119faae95683abee9a\",\"size_bytes\":2151,\"source_description\":\"Indian Express article captured via web.open during plaintiff merits investigation.\",\"source_url\":\"https://indianexpress.com/article/world/us-news/iran-closes-airspace-trump-cancels-plans-us-military-strikes-rubio-india-10704692/\",\"storage_name\":\"a7/a701f560aa648b724e0f3c4e0435fc666cb1905bad5650119faae95683abee9a\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Indian Express May 23 2026 Iran western airspace report\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-19T21:38:46Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_c909c4e71960_submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-c909c4e71960\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-c909c4e71960.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Contains the raw NOTAM text and interpretation for OIIX A1010/26, the core source for the alleged Iran-initiated closure effective May 22-25, 2026.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-19T21:39:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"c909c4e719606de87221b5ae5da7b8a15936e3dba215f3859d3eafb87cd3e16f\",\"size_bytes\":1690,\"source_description\":\"Notamify page for Tehran FIR/OIIX NOTAM A1010/26, captured via web.open during plaintiff merits investigation.\",\"source_url\":\"https://notamify.com/notams/OIIX/693f2d0f-54d3-433b-8128-49f5475ba269\",\"storage_name\":\"c9/c909c4e719606de87221b5ae5da7b8a15936e3dba215f3859d3eafb87cd3e16f\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintif